📍italiapastaepizza // 18821 W Arrow Hwy, Covina, CA  91722 United States

When in Coronado [Island] (San Diego), @LobsterWest is the place to be at 🔥 I didn’t know what to get so I just got everything 🤷🏻‍♂️ pictured are their Shrimp, Crab, and Lobster Rolls. 🗣 CHECK THEM OUT 🦐🦀🦞 👉🏼 Follow @tradefoods for more, & TAG YOUR FRIENDS👇🏼
📍@LobsterWest 1033 B Ave, Coronado, CA 92118
